==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Translator
<hw>Trans*lat"or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>translator</ets>: cf. F. <ets>translateur</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who translates; esp., one who renders into another language;
one who expresses the sense of words in one language by equivalent words
in another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Teleg.)</fld> <def>A repeating instrument.</def>
<mark>[Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Translatorship</ent>⟦br⟧
